- Create an object for the shape (either rectangle, triangle or square)
- Get input based on type of shape
  - length (l) & height (h) for rectangle
  - base (l), height (h), & lengths of sides (l, y, z) for triangle
  - length (l) for square
  - validate input to make sure it is a double
- Calculate 
  - perimeter
    - rectangle: 2l + 2h
    - triangle: l + y + z
    - square: 4l
  - area
    - rectangle: l * h
    - triangle: (l * h)/2
    - square: l^2
- Display area and perimeter of the given shape
